  "reverse": {
    "description": "Illyinska (St. Elias) Church in Subotiv village was built in 1653 as a Khmelnytskyi family burial-vault. B. Khmelnytskyi and his son Tymosh are buried there.",
    "lettering": "5\r\n5\r\n1994\r\nНАЦІОНАЛЬНИЙ БАНК УКРАЇНИ\r\nЦерква в селі Суботів\r\nП'ЯТЬ ГРИВЕНЬ\r\n5\r\n5",
